": {"name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，艾澤爾，我剛買的杯子蛋糕，你拿去吃吧，別想那麼多了！", "name": "笑呵呵的鄰居"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "公證所的事再怎麼麻煩，也只是份工作而已，下班了就別想啦！你不是還在實訓嗎，天塌下來有高個子頂著，別為難自己啦！", "name": "笑呵呵的鄰居"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開心點，別這麼無精打采的，不值得不值得！", "name": "笑呵呵的鄰居"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不值得嗎......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還在想呢......哈哈，那我先走啦。", "name": "笑呵呵的鄰居"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_366_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你的蛋糕。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個再普通不過的清晨，大街上行人還稀少。"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，再過一會兒，就會變成平常的樣子了吧，熱熱鬧鬧，吵吵嚷嚷。"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭人的生活......不就是這樣。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不要來個可麗餅？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，不用了......蛋糕還......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你？！", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#3$1"}, {"id": 3