acter", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她也許需要你。", "name": "安多恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_351_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我只是個普通人。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來挺丟臉的。雖然我之前一直在塞茜莉亞面前逞英雄，說什麼答應了就一定會做到，丟了工作也無所謂......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但昨天回家之後，我後怕了一夜。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "混血薩科塔、墮天使、萬國信使、大教堂的會議、薩卡茲、奇怪的異端組織......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼會和這些事情扯上關係的？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我原本只是想要一份體面的工作，最好能分到文職崗，按時上班，到點下班，安安穩穩度過一生......不是很好嗎？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾天的一切只不過是個插曲，能及時抽身難道不算我運氣好？幾十年之後再拿出來和朋友吹噓......", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#7$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣不就行了嗎？", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#5$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也許我現在也不該和你說話，我該轉身就走的。", "name": "艾澤爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4036_forcer_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}},