vg_npc_352_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要讓我去大教堂嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大教堂？不，不，塞茜莉亞，我不能讓你去大教堂。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你不去大教堂，別落到那個老傢伙手裡，去哪裡都可以。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來覺得安多恩把你帶走挺好的，既然他改了主意，那我自己來也無妨。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我如果去了大教堂，會有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "塞茜莉亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_352_1#1$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好說啊，塞茜莉亞，不好說。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我是很看重你的，知道嗎？費莉亞和我是朋友，雖然是很久以前了......", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總而言之，你的存在比你的小腦袋瓜能琢磨的事情要有用得多了。只要發揮得當......你能讓拉特蘭危如累卵。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟你是薩卡茲，卻又成了薩科塔。", "name": "奧倫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_355_1#4$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_355_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"cont